spec_data.Name: perl-IO-Event
spec_data.Description:
IO::Event provides a object-based callback system for handling nonblocking
IO. The design goal is to provide a system that just does the right thing
w/o the user needing to think about it much.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 12:29:35 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Tied filehandles for nonblocking IO with object callbacks
